    <item>
      <title>随着价格集会，中国中央银行购买了第五个月的黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-s-central-bank-buys-gold-for-fifth-month-as-prices-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国中央银行在3月连续第五个月增加了黄金，加深了对全球贸易和地缘政治动荡不断增长的避风港资产的赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-s-central-bank-buys-gold-for-fifth-month-as-prices-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 02:20:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易敏感的澳大利亚资产下降，因为风险情绪螺旋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trade-sensitive-australian-assets-drop-as-risk-sentiment-spirals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚依靠贸易的资产扩大了崩溃，投资者继续权衡唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税，因为总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯表示，他的政府将继续与美国互动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trade-sensitive-australian-assets-drop-as-risk-sentiment-spirals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 02:15:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战争的增长减缓的恐惧，中国市场卷起了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者为全球两个最大经济体之间螺旋式贸易冲突的影响，中国股票下跌，债券收益率降低了创纪录的低谷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:30:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾第一个托管交易日的前往熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/tsmc-slumps-10-on-tariff-woes-as-taiwan-returns-from-holiday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾的股票指数记录在案最多，在假期后恢复了熊市，这使它在熊市的轨道上走上了正轨，并抓住了唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税远足触发的全球抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/tsmc-slumps-10-on-tariff-woes-as-taiwan-returns-from-holiday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:08:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币陷入亚洲，加密货币感到贸易战痛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/bitcoin-btc-plunges-into-asia-open-as-crypto-feels-trade-war-pain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币在亚洲的一周中迅速卖出，强调了整个市场上明显的冒险情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/bitcoin-btc-plunges-into-asia-open-as-crypto-feels-trade-war-pain</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:37:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着关税风险触发避风港的竞标，中国的债券激增，减轻了赌注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-bonds-surge-as-tariff-risks-trigger-haven-bid-easing-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的政府债券飙升，将基准收益率推向了记录下最低的，因为由于担心美国关税和货币宽松的赌注，投资者急于避风港资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-bonds-surge-as-tariff-risks-trigger-haven-bid-easing-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 00:18:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票火山口，国库在关税动荡上集会：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球股票的飞行加速了，投资者堆积在避风港资产中，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税加深了中国宣布报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税升级嘎嘎声市场时，金属爪子损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/gold-falls-further-at-open-as-traders-assess-tariff-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜和其他金属逆转了早期的跌落，该跌落追踪了整个市场的残酷抛售，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的扩大贸易战击败了全球经济的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/gold-falls-further-at-open-as-traders-assess-tariff-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:17:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
